<br>
I use 2hs (or 2hb) quite a bit in order to reduce riposte damage.  I sometimes use it in exp groups when we don't have slowing, other times I use it on named mobs after I proc EB a few times (simply to save the clerics and druids some mana).<br>
<br>
Although it would be nice to have that 2hs from RZ (Blade of War) or New Hate, or even the one with Taunting Blow from Sol Ro Tower, I use that 2hb from BoT and it performs fairly well (I have trained Flurry 3, Punishing Blade 3, and Raging Flurry 3).  In fact, I used the 2hb from BoT and successfully tanked Mithaniel Marr (stun proc aggro).  I still use that thing to tank lots of Elemental and pre-Elemental named mobs.  <br>
<br>
Ghetto? You bet.  Effective....it's not half bad,<br>
